{"tid":1952882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（回帶）張建宗稱正安排逾3千萬口罩供應零售市場","createTime":"2020-04-01T01:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T03:43:58.000Z","uid":103981,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2be35fc776849e7794088031dd5bea1d06bbde","tid":1952882,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:10:32.000Z","msg":"張建宗稱正安排逾3千萬口罩供應零售市場<br />\n2020-01-30 HKT 22:50<br />\n<br />\n在疫情持續下，市面口罩供應緊張。政務司司長張建宗傍晚說，正安排超過3000萬個口罩供應零售市場，部分會先行應市。另外，會找人協助，讓懲教處工場24小時運作，提高口罩生產量。<br />\n<br />\n至於「港人優先」買口罩是否可行，政府指，外地人來港買口罩暫時數目不大，按身份限購亦有困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505746-20200130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505746-20200130.htm&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ae58c891\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505746-20200130.htm&h=07aaca10\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505746-20200130.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a40ec099d31e89972af511804514c2a3529e616","tid":1952882,"uid":119609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手到先定政府口罩到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4fab8cd1f659ad046a1474e0a1f220f1942ecf","tid":1952882,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"真係有3千萬隻又夠香港人頂幾耐"},{"pid":"09574c8759ad33f20e78171027ca60baa85aea20","tid":1952882,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4fab8cd1f659ad046a1474e0a1f220f1942ecf","tid":1952882,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"真係有3千萬隻又夠香港人頂幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:17:13.000Z","msg":"比左醫護先啦"},{"pid":"c04b1ced3fc324151637a1448b03e7354781a303","tid":1952882,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"